properties.Name: MedicalTestReferenceRange
properties.Description: The range of values that 95% of the identified population (age, sex, race) will exhibit for the associated medical test.

Columns.Name: MedicalTestTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Medical Test Type.

Columns.Name: MinimumAge
Columns.Description: Minimum Age to which this Reference Range applies.

Columns.Name: MaximumAge
Columns.Description: Maximum Age to which this Reference Range applies.

Columns.Name: SexId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Sex.

Columns.Name: RacialCategoryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Racial Category.

Columns.Name: ReferenceRangeMinimumValue
Columns.Description: The target or desired MIN-max reference range value.

Columns.Name: ReferenceRangeMaximumValue
Columns.Description: The target or desired min-MAX reference range value.

Columns.Name: ReferenceRangeMeanValue
Columns.Description: The mean value of the reference range.

Columns.Name: UnitOfMeasureId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: MedicalTestReferenceRangeNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the reference range.
